name: Pennzoil Gearplus 80W-90 GL-5

localDocs.name: Pzl Gear 80W-90 (GL-5) United States EN 140002686046 EHS V4.2 22-JAN-2020

marketing: PENNZOIL^® GEARPLUS^® SAE 80W-90 GL-5 gives the full protection of SAE 90 under high temperatures and hard driving conditions, while still providing the fast flow characteristics of SAE 80W when cold. This offers maximum lubrication and gear protection over a wide temperature range.
